				<p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://www.wordpress.com.tw/?cat=7" title="View all posts in 網誌" rel="category">網誌</a> | <a href="http://www.wordpress.com.tw/?p=135#respond" title="Comment on 自製圖片外框式樣">No Comments &#187;</a></p>
